<p>
Thanks for the letter, and thank you for sharing (or &quot;anti-sharing&quot;,
as you call it &#8212; cute phrase).
It's good for other people to hear about the goings-on in there.
<p>
You know, it just occurred to me that the people who really have
&quot;spiritual recoveries&quot; or &quot;spiritual awakenings&quot; are the
people who refuse to go along with the immoral and unspiritual behavior.
<p>
Oh well, have a good day anyway.
<p>
== Orange
