should I pray to something that doesn't exist and in which I have
absolutely no belief? I've thought through these things through time
and time again. I was raised as a Christian and even went to a church
school for 7 years, taking religion classes and attending chapel
every day. (It was a combination of world history and religion
classes that cemented my atheism.)

<p>
