Okay, I'm going to turn my life and my will over to MY DOG. Yeah,
that makes perfect sense.  I might lead us into homelessness because
I spent all my time playing with my dog and taking her for rides, but
my dog would get steaks every night, per her will. How that was going
to keep me sober, or help me deal with my alcoholic boyfriend, was
