totally false when applied to me (I was NOT powerless over alcohol,
my life was NOT unmanageable, I did NOT believe that a power greater
than myself was the only way to give me sanity, and I was NOT going
to turn my life and my will over to my dog, Zeus, Hera, Buddha,
Orion, Dionysus, or that 30,000 year old dude that Scientologists
believe in &#8212; Xenu?), I realized that Al-Anon really didn't have
anything to offer me other than stuff that I totally disagreed with.
